These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
Job: accountant, journalist
1. Job:accountant is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Job   | journalist | accountant |

 #################################
 
